text.tspan: Suicide rates among young people, 2000 to 2019
Number of deaths by suicide per 100,000 individuals in each age group. Suicide deaths are underreported in many
countries due to social stigma and cultural or legal concerns.
Data source: WHO, Global Health Estimates (2020)
